                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_844">p. 844</ref>, records
                    that Roosevelt and Churchill conferred from 11 p.m. until midnight. No record of
                    the discussion has been found. With reference to the meeting at 10 p.m. which
                    preceded this conference, in which the Log states that Roosevelt, Hull, and Eden
                    took part, see <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_930">p. 930</ref>,
                    fn. 1.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
